---
import BaseLayout from '../../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../../../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
import { getHreflang } from '../../../../i18n/hreflang';

const hreflang = getHreflang('/providers/vultr/');

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Review',
  name: 'Vultr Dify Hosting Review 2026',
  description: 'Vultr High Frequency VPS offre prestazioni NVMe in 32 sedi globali per hosting Dify. Da $12/mese per 4GB RAM.',
  reviewRating: {
    '@type': 'Rating',
    ratingValue: '4.2',
    bestRating: '5',
    worstRating: '1',
  },
  author: { '@type': 'Organization', name: 'Dify Hosting' },
  itemReviewed: {
    '@type': 'SoftwareApplication',
    name: 'Vultr Cloud Compute',
    url: 'https://www.vultr.com',
    applicationCategory: 'Cloud Hosting',
  },
  datePublished: '2026-01-01',
  dateModified: '2026-03-01',
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Vultr Dify Hosting Review 2026 — 32 Sedi in Tutto il Mondo"
  description="Vultr High Frequency VPS offre prestazioni NVMe in 32 sedi globali per hosting Dify. Da $12/mese per 4GB RAM. Ideale per distribuzioni mondiali."
  lang="it"
  canonical="https://dify-hosting.com/it/providers/vultr/"
  hreflang={hreflang}
  schema={schema}
  keywords="Vultr Dify hosting, Vultr VPS Dify, High Frequency NVMe Dify, Vultr 32 sedi, deploy Dify Vultr"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section hero-gradient">
    <div class="container-sm">
      <Breadcrumb items={[
        { label: 'Home', href: '/it/' },
        { label: 'Provider', href: '/it/best-dify-hosting/' },
        { label: 'Vultr' },
      ]} />

      <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:1.25rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        <div style="width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid #E5E7EB;background:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:10px;flex-shrink:0;"><img src="/logos/vultr-logo.svg" alt="vultr logo" width="36" height="36" style="object-fit:contain;" /></div>
        <div style="flex:1;min-width:200px;">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.75rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
            <span class="badge badge-primary">Più Sedi Globali</span>
            <span style="color:#6B7280;font-size:0.85rem;">Recensione Provider</span>
          </div>
          <h1 style="font-size:clamp(1.6rem,4vw,2.4rem);font-weight:800;color:#111827;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
            Vultr Dify Hosting Review 2026
          </h1>
          <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:1.05rem;">32 sedi globali con prestazioni NVMe. Ideale per team con utenti in tutto il mondo.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Riga valutazione -->
      <div class="card" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;gap:1.5rem;padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.25rem;">
          <div class="stars" aria-label="4.2 su 5 stelle">
            <span class="filled">★</span><span class="filled">★</span><span class="filled">★</span><span class="filled">★</span><span class="empty">★</span>
          </div>
          <span style="font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;">4,2<span style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#6B7280;">/5</span></span>
          <span style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#6B7280;font-weight:500;">La Nostra Valutazione</span>
        </div>
        <div style="width:1px;height:48px;background:#E2E8F0;flex-shrink:0;" class="hide-mobile"></div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.6rem;flex:1;">
          <span class="spec-chip">💰 Da $12/mese</span>
          <span class="spec-chip">🧠 4GB RAM</span>
          <span class="spec-chip">⚡ 2 vCPU</span>
          <span class="spec-chip">💾 65GB NVMe</span>
          <span class="spec-chip">🌍 32 Sedi</span>
          <span class="spec-chip">⏱️ Fatturazione Oraria</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://filedesign.com/go/vultr?ref=dify-hosting.com" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">
          Distribuisci su Vultr →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Panoramica -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-sm prose">
      <h2>Panoramica</h2>
      <p>
        Le 32 sedi di data center di Vultr lo rendono l'opzione più distribuita geograficamente per il hosting Dify. I piani High Frequency NVMe offrono eccellenti prestazioni I/O, e la fatturazione oraria consente di avviare e fermare le istanze secondo le necessità. Sebbene leggermente più costoso di Hetzner, la copertura globale di Vultr e l'IPv4 dedicato lo rendono ideale per team con utenti su più continenti.
      </p>
      <p>
        Per la maggior parte dei carichi di lavoro Dify consigliamo di iniziare con il <strong>piano High Frequency 2 vCPU / 4GB RAM a $18/mese</strong>. Questo offre I/O NVMe, RAM sufficiente per eseguire lo stack Docker di Dify, e margine per elaborazione documenti moderata e chiamate API LLM.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tabella Piani -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container-sm">
      <span class="section-label">Prezzi</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Piani Vultr per Dify</h2>
      <p style="color:#4B5563;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Tutti i piani includono IPv4 dedicato. I piani NVMe offrono I/O notevolmente migliore per il database vettoriale di Dify.</p>
      <div style="overflow-x:auto;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
        <table class="comparison-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Tipo</th>
              <th>vCPU</th>
              <th>RAM</th>
              <th>Storage</th>
              <th>Prezzo</th>
              <th>Note</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Cloud Compute Regular</td>
              <td>1</td>
              <td>2GB</td>
              <td>55GB SSD</td>
              <td class="price">$6/mese</td>
              <td><span class="cross">❌</span> Troppo piccolo</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Cloud Compute Regular</td>
              <td>2</td>
              <td>4GB</td>
              <td>80GB SSD</td>
              <td class="price">$12/mese</td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span> Minimo</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="background:#F0F7FF;">
              <td><strong>High Frequency</strong> ⭐</td>
              <td><strong>2</strong></td>
              <td><strong>4GB</strong></td>
              <td><strong>65GB NVMe</strong></td>
              <td class="price"><strong>$18/mese</strong></td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span> <strong>Consigliato</strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>High Frequency</td>
              <td>4</td>
              <td>8GB</td>
              <td>128GB NVMe</td>
              <td class="price">$36/mese</td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span> Produzione</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Optimized Cloud</td>
              <td>2</td>
              <td>4GB</td>
              <td>50GB NVMe</td>
              <td class="price">$28/mese</td>
              <td><span class="check">✅</span> Bassa latenza</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pro e Contro -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-sm">
      <span class="section-label">Valutazione</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Pro e Contro</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:1.25rem;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:#16A34A;margin-bottom:1rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;">
            <span>✅</span> Pro
          </h3>
          <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.6rem;">
            <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;color:#374151;font-size:0.9rem;"><span style="color:#16A34A;flex-shrink:0;">+</span> 32 sedi di data center globali</li>
            <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;color:#374151;font-size:0.9rem;"><span style="color:#16A34A;flex-shrink:0;">+</span> Istanze High Frequency NVMe</li>
            <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;color:#374151;font-size:0.9rem;"><span style="color:#16A34A;flex-shrink:0;">+</span> Fatturazione oraria — avvia e ferma liberamente</li>
            <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;color:#374151;font-size:0.9rem;"><span style="color:#16A34A;flex-shrink:0;">+</span> IPv6 incluso su tutte le istanze</li>
            <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;color:#374151;font-size:0.9rem;"><span style="color:#16A34A;flex-shrink:0;">+</span> Block Storage aggiuntivo disponibile</li>
            <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;color:#374151;font-size:0.9rem;"><span style="color:#16A34A;flex-shrink:0;">+</span> Opzione Kubernetes Gestito</li>
            <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;color:#374151;font-size:0.9rem;"><span style="color:#16A34A;flex-shrink:0;">+</span> Protezione DDoS inclusa</li>
            <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;color:#374151;font-size:0.9rem;"><span style="color:#16A34A;flex-shrink:0;">+</span> Eccellenti API e strumenti CLI</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:#DC2626;margin-bottom:1rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;">
            <span>❌</span> Contro
          </h3>
          <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.6rem;">
            <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;color:#374151;font-size:0.9rem;"><span style="color:#DC2626;flex-shrink:0;">−</span> Più costoso di Hetzner per distribuzioni EU</li>
            <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;color:#374151;font-size:0.9rem;"><span style="color:#DC2626;flex-shrink:0;">−</span> Nessuna opzione EU dedicata al GDPR</li>
            <li style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;color:#374151;font-size:0.9rem;"><span style="color:#DC2626;flex-shrink:0;">−</span> La qualità del supporto può variare per regione</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Guida all'installazione -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container-sm">
      <span class="section-label">Per Iniziare</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Come Distribuire Dify su Vultr</h2>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
        {[
          { n: 1, title: 'Crea un account Vultr', desc: 'Registrati su vultr.com e aggiungi un metodo di pagamento.' },
          { n: 2, title: 'Distribuisci un\'istanza High Frequency', desc: 'Seleziona High Frequency, Ubuntu 22.04, piano 2 vCPU / 4GB RAM.' },
          { n: 3, title: 'Scegli la sede più vicina ai tuoi utenti', desc: 'Vultr offre 32 sedi — scegli quella più vicina al tuo team o agli utenti finali.' },
          { n: 4, title: 'Accedi via SSH all\'istanza', desc: 'Usa l\'IP e le credenziali root dalla dashboard Vultr per connetterti.' },
          { n: 5, title: 'Installa Docker e Docker Compose', desc: 'Esegui lo script di installazione ufficiale Docker e aggiungi docker-compose-plugin.' },
          { n: 6, title: 'Clona il repository Dify', desc: 'git clone https://github.com/langgenius/dify.git && cd dify/docker' },
          { n: 7, title: 'Configura il file .env', desc: 'Copia .env.example in .env e imposta SECRET_KEY più le chiavi API LLM necessarie.' },
          { n: 8, title: 'Avvia Dify', desc: 'docker compose up -d — attendi ~2 minuti per l\'inizializzazione di tutti i container.' },
          { n: 9, title: 'Configura il firewall', desc: 'Usa ufw per consentire solo le porte 80/443. Blocca la 5001 e le altre porte interne.' },
        ].map(step => (
          <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
            <div class="step-number">{step.n}</div>
            <div class="card" style="flex:1;padding:1rem 1.25rem;">
              <p style="font-weight:600;color:#111827;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">{step.title}</p>
              <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:0.875rem;margin:0;">{step.desc}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Verdetto + CTA -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-sm">
      <div class="card card-featured" style="text-align:center;padding:2.5rem;">
        <span class="section-label">Il Nostro Verdetto</span>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;margin:0.5rem 0 1rem;">Migliore per Distribuzioni Globali</h2>
        <p style="color:#4B5563;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 1.75rem;">
          La scelta migliore quando si necessita di server vicini agli utenti a livello globale. Le 32 sedi offrono la massima flessibilità tra tutti i provider in questo confronto. I piani NVMe High Frequency sono adatti alle esigenze I/O di Dify.
        </p>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <a href="https://filedesign.com/go/vultr?ref=dify-hosting.com" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">
            Distribuisci su Vultr →
          </a>
          <a href="/it/best-dify-hosting/" class="btn-secondary">Confronta Tutti i Provider</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Link interni -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container-sm">
      <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:#111827;margin-bottom:1rem;">Guide Correlate</h2>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.75rem;">
        <a href="/it/best-dify-hosting/" class="btn-secondary" style="font-size:0.875rem;">Miglior Hosting Dify 2026</a>
        <a href="/it/providers/hetzner/" class="btn-secondary" style="font-size:0.875rem;">Recensione Hetzner</a>
        <a href="/it/providers/digitalocean/" class="btn-secondary" style="font-size:0.875rem;">Recensione DigitalOcean</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
